GENDA ITEM NO. 14 WAS PULLED FOR SEPARATE DISCUSSION AND 
CONSIDERATION 
14. Budget Calendar and Community Engagement Plan for Fiscal Year 2025-26
vote.description:
Department(s): Finance and Management Services 
Recommended Action: Approve the Budget Calendar and Community 
Engagement Plan for Fiscal Year 2025-26 (FY25-26). 
MINUTES: Councilmember Lopez requested a yearly practice regarding the 
involvement of a Youth Forum and partnership with the local school district. 
Councilmember Penaloza requested the involvement of multiple school districts. 
MOTION: Councilmember Lopez moved to approve the recommended action 
for Agenda Item No. 14, seconded by Councilmember Hernandez. 
The motion carried, 7-0, by the following roll call vote:
